(197, 59, '1.	_______________ is the systematic identification of the physical, chemical, and toxicological properties of petroleum waste streams', 'Waste characterization', 1, '2026-03-09 06:34:53'),
(198, 59, '2.	Petroleum waste streams can be classified based on their origin in the petroleum value chain (upstream, midstream, downstream), their physical  state (solid, liquid, gaseous), and their _______________ (hazardous vs non-hazardous).', 'Hazard potential', 1, '2026-03-09 06:38:27'),
