(201, 59, '5.	______________ are a major waste stream in petroleum operations and include both intentional releases (e.g., flaring, venting) and unintentional releases (e.g., fugitive emissions, equipment leaks).', 'Gaseous emissions', 1, '2026-03-09 06:41:31'),
