(62, 32, 'In Northern Nigeria, when conducting focus groups on sensitive topics, the culturally appropriate approach is often:', 'Mixed-gender groups with a male facilitator', 'Gender-separate sessions with same-gender facilitators', 'Large public gatherings', 'Individual written surveys only', 'B', 2, '2026-03-02 19:13:20', '2026-03-02 19:13:20'),
