umber: 1310206641\r\n\r\nBank: Zenith Bank\r\n\r\nAfter payment, please email your proof of payment (bearing your full name and programme) to wmsr@fupre.edu.ng\r\n, and submit a printed copy to the Centreâ€™s office for verification.\r\n\r\nKindly ensure that your acceptance fee is paid within two (2) weeks from the date of this email to secure your admission. Failure to do so may result in forfeiture of your offer.\r\n\r\nWe warmly welcome you to our vibrant academic community and look forward to guiding you through a rewarding research journey.\r\n\r\nFor further enquiries, please contact us via wmsr@fupre.edu.ng\r\n or visit the Centreâ€™s office during working hours.\r\n\r\nWarm regards,\r\n\r\nMr Ibuwa Ogundimu\r\nHead, Admissions office, \r\nCentre for Waste Management and Sustainable Resources, \r\nFederal University of Petroleum Resources\r\nEffurun, Delta State, Nigeria.', 1, 'inbox', NULL, '2025-10-29 00:05:05', ''),
(38, 'CWMSR', 'admin@cwmsrfupre.com.ng', 'alakasodiq@cwmsrfupre.com.ng', 'Re: Congratulations on Your Admission to the Doctoral Programme â€“ FUPRE Centre for Waste Management and Sustainable Resources', 'Good morning Mr Sodiq,\r\n\r\nI appreciate your email.\r\nIt is a generic letter, ignore the physical evidence at the Centre office.\r\nJust send the proof to the email suggested in the email sent to you.\r\n\r\nRegards,\r\n\r\nMrs Ibuwa Ogundimu\r\n\r\n--- Original Message ---\r\n\r\n\r\n--- Original Message ---\r\nFrom: Sodiq Adedamola Alaka <alakasodiq@cwmsrfupre.com.ng>\r\nSent: 2025-10-29 01:05:05\r\nSubject: Re: Congratulations on Your Admission to the Doctoral Programme â€“ FUPRE Centre for Waste Management and Sustainable Resources\r\n\r\nDear Sir/Ma,\r\n\r\nThank you for your email and the offer of admission into the Professional Doctoral Programme at the Centre for Waste Management and Sustainable Resources. I am grateful for the opportunity.\r\n\r\nI currently reside outside Nigeria and applied for the programme because it accommodates distance learning. I would like to confirm whether the programme can be completed fully online or if physical attendance at the Centre is required at any stage.\r\n\r\nIf in-person attendance is mandatory, I may need to reconsider my enrolment due to my current location.\r\n\r\nI look forward to your clarification.\r\n\r\nKind regards,\r\nSodiq Adedamola Alaka\r\n\r\n\r\n--- Original Message ---\r\n\r\n\r\n--- Original Message ---\r\nFrom: CWMSR <admin@cwmsrfupre.com.ng>\r\nSent: 2025-10-28 14:27:37\r\nSubject: Congratulations on Your Admission to the Doctoral Programme â€“ FUPRE Centre for Waste Management and Sustainable Resources\r\n\r\nSodiq Adedamola Alaka,\r\n\r\nWarm greetings from the Centre for Waste Management and Sustainable Resources,\r\nFederal University of Petroleum Resources, Effurun (FUPRE).\r\n\r\nWe are delighted to inform you that you have been successfully admitted into the Professional Doctoral Programme at our Centre for the 2025/2026 Academic Session.\r\n\r\nAttached to this email is your official offer letter of provisional admission, which contains full details of your financial obligations and registration process. Kindly read the letter carefully and adhere to all instructions.\r\n\r\nPlease note the following payment details:\r\n\r\nTotal Payable Fees: â‚¦735,000 (Acceptance, Administrative, Examination, and School Fees inclusive)\r\n\r\nAccount Name: Centre for Waste Management and Sustainable Resources\r\n\r\nAccount Number: 1310206641\r\n\r\nBank: Zenith Bank\r\n\r\nAfter payment, please email your proof of payment (bearing your full name and programme) to wmsr@fupre.edu.ng\r\n, and submit a printed copy to the Centreâ€™s office for verification.\r\n\r\nKindly ensure that your acceptance fee is paid within two (2) weeks from the date of this email to secure your admission. Failure to do so may result in forfeiture of your offer.\r\n\r\nWe warmly welcome you to our vibrant academic community and look forward to guiding you through a rewarding research journey.\r\n\r\nFor further enquiries, please contact us via wmsr@fupre.edu.ng\r\n or visit the Centreâ€™s office during working hours.\r\n\r\nWarm regards,\r\n\r\nMr Ibuwa Ogundimu\r\nHead, Admissions office, \r\nCentre for Waste Management and Sustainable Resources, \r\nFederal University of Petroleum Resources\r\nEffurun, Delta State, Nigeria.', 1, 'inbox', NULL, '2025-10-29 06:21:33', ''),
(39, 'Sodiq Adedamola Alaka', 'alakasodiq@cwmsrfupre.com.ng', 'wmsr@fupre.edu.ng', 'Proof of Payment for Acceptance Fee â€“ Professional Doctoral Programme', 'Hello,\r\n\r\nI have paid the acceptance fee of â‚¦85,000 for the Professional Doctoral Programme at the Centre for Waste Management and Sustainable Resources.\r\n\r\nPayment details:\r\nâ€¢ Name: Sodiq Adedamola Alaka\r\nâ€¢ Programme: Professional Doctoral Programme\r\nâ€¢ Amount: â‚¦85,000\r\nâ€¢ Date of payment: 31/10/2025\r\n\r\nAttached is the proof of payment for your confirmation.\r\nPlease confirm receipt and advise on the next steps for registration.\r\n\r\nThank you.\r\n\r\nKind regards,\r\nSodiq Adedamola Alaka', 0, 'inbox', '[\"1761911633_Receipt-35133832618006844293.pdf\"]', '2025-10-31 11:53:53', 'alakasodiq@gmail.com'),
(40, 'OLAOLUWA OLAWE', 'olawe_laozy@cwmsrfupre.com.ng', 'admin@cwmsrfupre.com.ng', 'Re: Congratulations on Your Admission to the Professional Masterâ€™s Programme â€“ FUPRE Centre for Waste Management and Sustainable Resources', 'ACCEPTANCE FEE PAID\r\n\r\n--- Original Message ---\r\n\r\n\r\n--- Original Message ---\r\nFrom: CWMSR <admin@cwmsrfupre.com.ng>\r\nSent: 2025-10-28 15:23:47\r\nSubject: Congratulations on Your Admission to the Professional Masterâ€™s Programme â€“ FUPRE Centre for Waste Management and Sustainable Resources\r\n\r\nDear OLAOLUWA OLAWE,\r\nWarm greetings from the Centre for Waste Management and Sustainable Resources,\r\nFederal University of Petroleum Resources, Effurun (FUPRE).\r\n\r\nWe are pleased to inform you that you have been offered provisional admission into the Professional Masterâ€™s Programme of the Centre for the 2025/2026 Academic Session.\r\n\r\nAttached is your official admission letter, which provides detailed information about your financial commitments and next steps for registration. Kindly review it thoroughly and follow the given instructions.\r\n\r\nPlease take note of the following payment details:\r\n\r\nTotal Payable Fees: â‚¦535,000 (Acceptance, Administrative, Examination, and School Fees inclusive)\r\n\r\nAccount Name: Centre for Waste Management and Sustainable Resources\r\n\r\nAccount Number: 1310206641\r\n\r\nBank: Zenith Bank\r\n\r\nAfter making the payment, send your proof of payment (clearly stating your full name and programme) to wmsr@fupre.edu.ng, and submit a hard copy to the Centreâ€™s office for verification.\r\n\r\nYou are required to pay your acceptance fee within two (2) weeks of this notification to secure your admission. Failure to do so will result in forfeiture of your slot.\r\n\r\nCongratulations once again on your admission. We look forward to supporting your growth and success throughout your postgraduate journey.\r\n\r\nWarm regards,\r\n\r\nMr Ibuwa Ogundimu\r\nHead, Admissions office, \r\nCentre for Waste Management and Sustainable Resources, \r\nFederal University of Petroleum Resources\r\nEffurun, Delta State, Nigeria.', 1, 'inbox', '[\"1761940169_receipt-October-31st-2025-8-36-01-pm.jpg\"]', '2025-10-31 19:49:29', ''),
(41, 'CWMSR', 'admin@cwmsrfupre.com.ng', 'imeldablankson4u@cwmsrfupre.com.ng', 'Offer of admission', 'Dear Imelda Blankson,\r\nWe are delighted to inform you that you have been successfully admitted into the Professional Doctoral Programme at our Centre for the 2025/2026 Academic Session.\r\n\r\nAttached to this email is your official offer letter of provisional admission, which contains full details of your financial obligations and registration process. Kindly read the letter carefully and adhere to all instructions.\r\n\r\nPlease note the following payment details:\r\n\r\nTotal Payable Fees: â‚¦735,000 (Acceptance, Administrative, Examination, and School Fees inclusive)\r\n\r\nAccount Name: Centre for Waste Management and Sustainable Resources\r\n\r\nAccount Number: 1310206641\r\n\r\nBank: Zenith Bank\r\n\r\nAfter payment, please email your proof of payment (bearing your full name and programme) to wmsr@fupre.edu.ng\r\n, and submit a printed copy to the Centreâ€™s office for verification.\r\n\r\nKindly ensure that your acceptance fee is paid within two (2) weeks from the date of this email to secure your admission. Failure to do so may result in forfeiture of your offer.\r\n\r\nWe warmly welcome you to our vibrant academic community and look forward to guiding you through a rewarding research journey.\r\n\r\nFor further enquiries, please contact us via wmsr@fupre.edu.ng\r\nor visit the Centreâ€™s office during working hours.\r\n\r\nWarm regards,\r\n\r\nMrs Ibuwa Ogundimu\r\nHead, Admissions office,\r\nCentre for Waste Management and Sustainable Resources,\r\nFederal University of Petroleum Resources\r\nEffurun, Delta State, Nigeria', 1, 'inbox', '[\"1762350429_IMELDA_TAIYE__BLANKSON-PhD.doc\"]', '2025-11-05 13:47:24', ''),
