(44, 'IMELDA TAIYE, BLANKSON', 'imeldablankson4u@cwmsrfupre.com.ng', 'wmsr@fupre.edu.ng', 'Receipt of payment', 'Good day,\r\n\r\nI hope this email finds you well.\r\n\r\nFind attached the receipt of payment for the professional Doctoral Programme at the Centre for Waste Management and Sustainable Resources, Federal University of Petroleum Resources, Effurun, for Imelda Blankson.\r\n\r\nThank you.\r\n\r\nBest regards,\r\nImelda Blankson', 0, 'inbox', '[\"1762669568_Receipt_of_payment_for_PhD_in_CWMSR_for_Imelda_Blankson.pdf\"]', '2025-11-09 06:26:08', ''),
