(39, 'Sodiq Adedamola Alaka', 'alakasodiq@cwmsrfupre.com.ng', 'CWMSR', 'admin@cwmsrfupre.com.ng', 'Re: Congratulations on Your Admission to the Doctoral Programme â€“ FUPRE Centre for Waste Management and Sustainable Resources', 'Dear Sir/Ma,\r\n\r\nThank you for your email and the offer of admission into the Professional Doctoral Programme at the Centre for Waste Management and Sustainable Resources. I am grateful for the opportunity.\r\n\r\nI currently reside outside Nigeria and applied for the programme because it accommodates distance learning. I would like to confirm whether the programme can be completed fully online or if physical attendance at the Centre is required at any stage.\r\n\r\nIf in-person attendance is mandatory, I may need to reconsider my enrolment due to my current location.\r\n\r\nI look forward to your clarification.\r\n\r\nKind regards,\r\nSodiq Adedamola Alaka\r\n\r\n\r\n--- Original Message ---\r\n\r\n\r\n--- Original Message ---\r\nFrom: CWMSR <admin@cwmsrfupre.com.ng>\r\nSent: 2025-10-28 14:27:37\r\nSubject: Congratulations on Your Admission to the Doctoral Programme â€“ FUPRE Centre for Waste Management and Sustainable Resources\r\n\r\nSodiq Adedamola Alaka,\r\n\r\nWarm greetings from the Centre for Waste Management and Sustainable Resources,\r\nFederal University of Petroleum Resources, Effurun (FUPRE).\r\n\r\nWe are delighted to inform you that you have been successfully admitted into the Professional Doctoral Programme at our Centre for the 2025/2026 Academic Session.\r\n\r\nAttached to this email is your official offer letter of provisional admission, which contains full details of your financial obligations and registration process. Kindly read the letter carefully and adhere to all instructions.\r\n\r\nPlease note the following payment details:\r\n\r\nTotal Payable Fees: â‚¦735,000 (Acceptance, Administrative, Examination, and School Fees inclusive)\r\n\r\nAccount Name: Centre for Waste Management and Sustainable Resources\r\n\r\nAccount Number: 1310206641\r\n\r\nBank: Zenith Bank\r\n\r\nAfter payment, please email your proof of payment (bearing your full name and programme) to wmsr@fupre.edu.ng\r\n, and submit a printed copy to the Centreâ€™s office for verification.\r\n\r\nKindly ensure that your acceptance fee is paid within two (2) weeks from the date of this email to secure your admission. Failure to do so may result in forfeiture of your offer.\r\n\r\nWe warmly welcome you to our vibrant academic community and look forward to guiding you through a rewarding research journey.\r\n\r\nFor further enquiries, please contact us via wmsr@fupre.edu.ng\r\n or visit the Centreâ€™s office during working hours.\r\n\r\nWarm regards,\r\n\r\nMr Ibuwa Ogundimu\r\nHead, Admissions office, \r\nCentre for Waste Management and Sustainable Resources, \r\nFederal University of Petroleum Resources\r\nEffurun, Delta State, Nigeria.', '2025-10-29 00:05:05', '', NULL),
