(60, 'Oritseweyinmi Erikowa-Orighoye', 'oritseweyinmi.erikowa-orighoye@cwmsrfupre.com.ng', 'Centurion Okon Awakessien', 'centurionawakessien@cwmsrfupre.com.ng', 'Continuous Assessment', 'Hello Everyone, \r\n\r\nI hope you are doing well. \r\n\r\nI have attached the document for your CA. \r\n\r\nIf you have questions, reach out to me. \r\n\r\nBest wishes\r\nWeyinmi Erikowa-Orighoye', '2026-01-20 13:11:35', 'mkiwunor@cwmsrfupre.com.ng,chuksvenantius@cwmsrfupre.com.ng', '[\"1768914695_ESW_815_Continuous_Assessment__CBR_Case_Study_Application_Portfolio__Weeks_1-5_.pdf\"]'),
